title.rendered: Sydney vs Brisbane, Australian T20 League, 2022: Today’s Match Preview, Fantasy Cricket Team

content.rendered:
We have opted for a fantasy cricket team based on the recent performances, overall impact, and credit points.

Probable XIs

Probable XI for Sydney: Alex Hales, Matthew Gilkes (wk), Rilee Rossouw, Oliver Davies, Daniel Sams, Alex Ross, Nathan McAndrew, Chris Green (c), Gurinder Sandhu, Brendan Doggett, Usman Qadir

Probable XI for Brisbane: Max Bryant, Colin Munro, Matt Renshaw, Sam Billings, Jimmy Peirson (c & wk), Ross Whiteley, Michael Neser, Xavier Barlett, Mark Steketee, Mitchell Swepson, Matthew Kuhnemann

Pitch Report

Venue: Sydney Showground Stadium, Sydney

(Based on the last game)

1st innings average score: 139

2nd innings average score: 15

Wickets per innings: 9

Type: Seamers are likely to get decent assistance from the wicket.

Weather: Clear.

Wins

Batting 1st: 100%

Batting 2nd: –%

Fantasy Tips of The Day

Out of the 19 wickets that fell at the venue between Adelaide and Sydney, 18 wickets belonged to the seamers.

In the same match, 6 catches were pouched by the wicketkeepers from both sides.

Sydney have played 4 games till now, but their spinners have managed only 1 wicket in the period.
